- To start a container image
  docker run -it --rm -v /home/ricardog/src/eec/predicts/data:/data:ro -v predicts-data:/out predicts:latest

- To create an NFS-mounted volume for predicts data

  docker volume create --driver local --opt type=nfs --opt o=addr=192.168.178.52,rw,nolock,soft,nfsvers=3 --opt device=:/mnt/Pool1/predicts-data predicts-data


- Start the postgis container
docker run --name postgis --restart unless-stopped -p 5432:5432 -e POSTGRES_PASSWORD=postgis -e POSTGRES_USER=postgis -e PGDATA=/var/lib/postgresql/data/pgdata -e POSTGIS_ENABLE_OUTDB_RASTERS=1 -e POSTGIS_GDAL_ENABLED_DRIVERS=ENABLE_ALL -v pgconf:/etc/postgresql -v postgis:/var/lib/postgresql/data/pgdata -v predicts-data:/mnt/predicts -v datasets:/mnt/data -d postgis/postgis:13-3.1

- Start jupyter notebook server on bonobo
  jupyter notebook --ip 192.168.0.46 --no-browser --ConnectionFileMixin.ip=192.168.0.46

- Compute area of raster grid:
https://gis.stackexchange.com/questions/127165/more-accurate-way-to-calculate-area-of-rasters#127327

- Compare FP numbers:
https://randomascii.wordpress.com/2012/02/25/comparing-floating-point-numbers-2012-edition/

- Income & welath inequality
https://www.chartbookofeconomicinequality.com

https://wid.world/data/

https://www.cbpp.org/research/poverty-and-inequality/a-guide-to-statistics-on-historical-trends-in-income-inequality#_ftn23

- Polity Project
http://www.systemicpeace.org/polityproject.html

- Cultural Proximity
https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0152979

- Moran's I test
https://mgimond.github.io/Spatial/spatial-autocorrelation-in-r.html

https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/spdep/vignettes/nb_igraph.html

- Ecological Land Units
https://rmgsc.cr.usgs.gov/ecosystems/

  Similar to http://maps.tnc.org/gis_data.html with higher level of detail.

- World Governance Indicators
  http://info.worldbank.org/governance/wgi/index.aspx#home

  wgidataset.xls

- Behrmann proj4 init string

  +proj=cea +lon_0=0 +lat_ts=30 +x_0=0 +y_0=0 +datum=WGS84 +ellps=WGS84 +units=m +no_defs

- Hill shade generation

  https://www.neonscience.org/create-hillshade-py

- To start qgis docker container

  docker run -v /mnt/gorilla/old/src/eec/predicts/data:/data:ro -v /mnt/gorilla/data:/datasets:ro -v predicts-data:/out -p 2200:22 -u root qgis:latest

  